ght controller:\n- Rotate on the left or right by using the joystick\n- Update the vertical offset (up or down) by using the joystick\n- Choose a location and teleport to it by using the virtual laser pointer\n- Teleport by using the index trigger only if the laser is green (not red)\n\nLeft controller:\n- Move continuously by using the joystick\n- Switch pannel and map by using the grip/hand trigger\n- If both map and pannel are disabled, switch between rendering modes (texturing or normal colors) by pressing the index trigger\n- The map shows the cloud of mesh vertices and the user location\n- If the pannel is enabled, switch between constrained and unconstrained motions by pressing the index trigger\n- The constrained motion controls your height above the ground\n- The pannel shows information about the 3D model and the selected motion.", "short_description": "Move continuously like a pedestrian in a snowy town, which was computed by photogrammetry from two 2496x2496 videos taken by a helmet-held camera (Garmin Virb 360) and by walking about 670 meters in a town (Laschamps, in France)."}]}, "developer_name": "Maxime Lhuillier", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://maximelhuillier.fr/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Unity 2019.4", "support_website_url": "http://maxime.lhuillier.free.fr/", "website_url": "https://maximelhuillier.fr/", "category": "ENTERTAINMENT", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "726368587961803"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["EXPLORATION"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING"], "supported_tracking